Nivel is an active member of the following networks:&#xd;
•	EUPHA – European Public Health Association. Represents European public health experts from research institutes, health policy makers and professionals. The Association has several sections on various public health topics with their own active member lists. The formal members of EUPHA are the National Public Health Associations. Nivel houses the administrative office of EUPHA.&#xd;
•	EFPC - European Forum of Primary Care. The aim of the Forum is to improve the health of the European population by promoting strong Primary Care. Nivel houses the administrative office of EFPC.&#xd;
•	HSPM - Health Systems and Policy Monitor Network, initiated by the European Observatory on Health Systems and Policies, is an innovative online platform that provides detailed description of health systems and provides up to data information on reforms and changes. Nivel contributes to the Dutch page. Furthermore, the Network initiates and collaborates in international comparative health services research.
